CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 3, 1954, pg. 7, reads: "Receives 'Orchid Award' - The Pittsburgh Pioneer Club presented its 'Orchid Award' to Mrs. Robert L. Vann at the Greene Hearthe [sic] Saturday.  Shown during the presentation are, left to right, Mrs. Lillian Woodyard Brown, president of the Pittsburgh Pioneers; Mrs. Vann and Mrs. Eleanor Monroe Jones. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three women, Lillian Woodyard Brown, Jessie Vann wearing hexagon patterned dress and corsage, and Eleanor Monroe Jones presenting Orchid Award from Pittsburgh Pioneer Club to Vann, at Greene Hearth, another version
